Since there are a couple new faces around here, I wanted to re-introduce myself.

My journey began in the world of reporting, but it was in interior design where my heart truly found its passion. From newsrooms to design studios, Ive learned the art of storytelling, and I know that every home should be a beautiful reflection of your unique story. 

As a mother of four and the proud wife of my talented contractor hubby Chad, I understand the importance of having a functional and efficient home that caters to the needs of a busy family. 

So whether its a cozy corner for reading, a kitchen that ignites culinary inspiration, or a living room that brings everyone together, my heart and soul go into crafting spaces that embrace the essence of who you are.

📸: @kerri.torrey
